Package net.viktorc.detroid.util

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Copiable<T>
    An interface declaring a method for deep-copying objects of the implementing class.
    Hashable
    An interface that defines a function for providing a 64 bit hash key that identifies the object and allows it to be hashed onto an index.
    LossyHashTable.Entry<T extends LossyHashTable.Entry<T>>
    An interface for hash table entries that implicitly extends the Comparable and Hashable interfaces.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ASGD
    An adaptive stochastic gradient descent implementation for supervised learning.
    BitOperations
    A static class exclusively for bitwise operations.
    GrayCode
    A utility class for gray coding integers and for converting gray coded numbers into their natural values.
    LossyHashTable<T extends LossyHashTable.Entry<T>>
    A generic hash table for statistical or turn-based game AI applications with massive storage requirements where losslessness is inefficient.
    MillerRabin
    Provides primality testing related functions based on the Miller-Rabin algorithm.
    PBIL
    An abstract Population-based Incremental Learning algorithm implementation for optimizing parameters represented by strings of binary digits.
    QuickSort
    An implementation of the quickSort algorithm to sort arrays of generic objects.
    SizeEstimator
    A singleton utility class for estimating the memory footprints of objects on the (HotSpot) JVM heap.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    SizeOf
    A simple enumeration type to help estimate the memory overhead of objects on the JVM heap.
